node.text:
In the latest episode on the LAW OF ATTRACTION SECRETS Podcast I talked with the 10X king himself @grantcardone 💸💸💸

We talked everything business, mindset and Scalability! 

You’ll learn:

✅ Why Entrepreneurs often fail to Scale

✅ How to quickly turn ideas into profits 

✅ Why Following your heart is wrong 😑 

✅ How to attach a scalability factor to your services and products 

✅ How to look at products and problems "Horizontally" instead of "Vertically"

And you’ll hear amazing stories from both Grant and My life! 

If you want to learn how to build a sustainable business that makes you millions, you need to listen to this podcast! This episode is like being one on one mentored by Grant himself!! 

I just want to say thank you for all of the support you guys and gals have been giving me and the podcast ♥️🙏🏼 It’s only because of YOU that I can do all of these amazing interviews, and bring MORE and more of this hidden knowledge to the world!

525,600 minutes a year 525,600 moments to be the best versions of ourselves for one another

node.text:
Our time on the ocean made me think how important it is to truly be the Captain of your own mind! And to navigate as best you can through life you need the best possible toolbox! 
80% of it is in the mindset and 20% is in the action. 
where are you spending your money?
What do you value the most? 
Most times I find people want something major but they’re not willing to put the major work into their mindset first to obtaining it. 
Invest into upgrading your mindset and you will upgrade your life! 
Wherever you focus your mind your energy flows.. 
✨🙏🏼

Alright HERE it is! 
Link is in my bio for my deep chat with world renowned Serial entrepreneur and author @russellbrunson founder of @clickfunnels !!!

Russell is sharing the strategies that created his success, like:

✅ How to build an audience online

✅ How to convert that audience to an email list

✅ The evolving morning routine that keeps him energetic and excited

✅ How to make MILLIONS from the right funnels!

node.text:
Don’t you just love children’s excitement and creative imaginations?! From being a single mom for so many years it taught me how to open my mind up to the pursuit of fun and happiness. Every day when I ask my son, what do you want to do today? he replies with; I want to play and have fun in the playground! This same excitement they have for the playground and play is the same excitement we as adults should have for life and all of life’s treasures. If we woke up every day seeking joy and excitement we would in turn receive situations, events and people into our life that match those feelings. Instead of letting the work or a stressful situation rule your life and dictate your day, wake up and seek activities, events and people that make you live from a place of your highest inspiration and excitement. 
.
Thank you for such a beautiful stay @hotelkensington for Rio’s birthday ♥️
